OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1783727306
OL,3,CArthur Fery's Wimbledon dream ended
OL,4,Cafter semi-final defeat to Alexander
OL,5,CZverev
OL,7,FArthur Fery's dreams of reaching the
OL,8,FWimbledon final came to an end after
OL,9,Fhis defeat to French Open champion
OL,10,FAlexander Zverev on Friday.
OL,12,FThe British wild card defied the odds
OL,13,Fwith his run to the last four as an
OL,14,Funheralded 23-year-old ranked 114.
OL,16,FFery walked off court to a standing
OL,17,Fovation, with his life-changing run
OL,18,Fpropelling him to 36th in the
OL,19,Frankings, making him the new British
OL,20,Fnumber one. His new rankings will be
OL,21,Fannounced on Monday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
