FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1783727306
OL,3,CArthur Fery's Wimbledon dream ended
OL,4,Cafter semi-final defeat to Alexander
OL,5,CZverev
OL,7,FFery, who celebrates his 24th birthday
OL,8,Fin two days, will also be taking home
OL,9,F#900,000 in prize money.
OL,11,FZverev was a significant step up from
OL,12,Fany of Fery's previous opponents and
OL,13,Fthe second seed powered his way to
OL,14,Fvictory.
OL,16,FHe becomes the first German man since
OL,17,FBoris Becker in 1995 to make the final
OL,18,Fhere, while he joins the select group
OL,19,Fof players to have reached the trophy
OL,20,Fmatch at each grand slam.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
