PN,30903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1783727306
OL,3,CArthur Fery's Wimbledon dream ended
OL,4,Cafter semi-final defeat to Alexander
OL,5,CZverev
OL,7,F"It's amazing," Zverev said of his
OL,8,Fachievement. "This grand slam has
OL,9,Falways been the one I struggled with
OL,10,Fthe most, now all of a sudden I'm in
OL,11,Fthe final of Wimbledon. Incredibly
OL,12,Fhappy, incredibly proud, but we've got
OL,13,Fone more match to go on Sunday."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
