PN,30904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1783727306
OL,3,CArthur Fery's Wimbledon dream ended
OL,4,Cafter semi-final defeat to Alexander
OL,5,CZverev
OL,7,FSpeaking of his opponent on Friday,
OL,8,FZverev said: "Arthur is an
OL,9,Funbelievable player. I think he's
OL,10,Fgoing to be a senior citizen on our
OL,11,Ftour because I think he's going to
OL,12,Fplay for 15 years plus and I really
OL,13,Fthink he's going to do amazing things
OL,14,Fin this sport."
OL,16,FThe 29-year-old, who will climb above
OL,17,FCarlos Alcaraz to become world number
OL,18,Ftwo on Monday, stands 6ft 6in tall
OL,19,Fcompared to Fery's 5ft 9in, and the
OL,20,Fchallenge was all too clear as the
OL,21,Fpair walked out onto Centre Court.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
