PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1783727306
OL,3,CArthur Fery's Wimbledon dream ended
OL,4,Cafter semi-final defeat to Alexander
OL,5,CZverev
OL,7,FHe was the fifth British man in the
OL,8,FOpen Era to reach the last four at
OL,9,FWimbledon, with only Andy Murray going
OL,10,Fon to make the final.
OL,12,FThe crowd were ready to play their
OL,13,Frole and cheered heartily when Fery
OL,14,Fgot on the board in the third point of
OL,15,Fthe match.
OL,17,FIt did not take long for Zverev to
OL,18,Fbreak through, opening up a 3-1 lead,
OL,19,Fbut back came Fery to level with a
OL,20,Fstrong backhand.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1783727306
OL,3,CArthur Fery's Wimbledon dream ended
OL,4,Cafter semi-final defeat to Alexander
OL,5,CZverev
OL,7,FFery complained to umpire Marijana
OL,8,FVeljovic over what he perceived as a
OL,9,Fmissed let call ` the same issue that
OL,10,Fhad riled up first-round opponent
OL,11,FDamir Dzumhur ` but he did not allow
OL,12,Fit to distract him.
OL,14,FThe Wimbledon resident kept pace, but
OL,15,Fdouble-faulted on the second point and
OL,16,Fthings went downhill from there.
OL,18,FZverev's serve was a strong weapon,
OL,19,Fbut it was sometimes his dodgy
OL,20,Fforehand that was doing a lot of the
OL,21,Fdamage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
