FL,310,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1783727306
OL,3,CArthur Fery's Wimbledon dream ended
OL,4,Cafter semi-final defeat to Alexander
OL,5,CZverev
OL,7,FFery was unfortunate that an over-
OL,8,Feager ball boy interrupted a point at
OL,9,F0-30 in the third game of the second
OL,10,Fset, although Zverev may well have hit
OL,11,Fa winner anyway, and a break of serve
OL,12,Fwas quickly followed by another that
OL,13,Fall but ended the set.
OL,15,FFery had been on court for nearly 16
OL,16,Fand a half hours in making it to the
OL,17,Flast four, three and a half hours more
OL,18,Fthan Zverev, and fatigue may well have
OL,19,Fbeen a factor, with his shots lacking
OL,20,Fthe vim that had overwhelmed Cobolli.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
