PN,30909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1783727306
OL,3,CArthur Fery's Wimbledon dream ended
OL,4,Cafter semi-final defeat to Alexander
OL,5,CZverev
OL,7,FHe at least gave the crowd a final
OL,8,Fflourish, recovering from 0-40 at 2-4
OL,9,Fwith five points in a row, but Zverev
OL,10,Fwrapped up victory in only two hours
OL,11,Fand 13 minutes to set up a meeting
OL,12,Fwith either Jannik Sinner or Novak
OL,13,FDjokovic on Sunday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
